the carbon dioxide released

00:07:46.470 --> 00:07:49.470
is absorbed by trees
through photosynthesis.

00:07:49.470 --> 00:07:51.530
The process is cyclical.

00:07:51.530 --> 00:07:53.560
The industry could
play a big role

00:07:53.560 --> 00:07:55.600
in reducing carbon
dioxide emissions

00:07:55.600 --> 00:07:58.620
by switching to renewable energy
for generating electricity.

